author: Reuters
title: 'First we need to stay alive': Chile's protests dampened by coronavirus
description: Chile's central square in Santiago, the country's capital of 6 million people, has quieted down after months of fiery protests as fear of coronavirus spreads.
content: SANTIAGO, Chile For many in Santiagos Plaza Italia, ground zero for mass protests in Chile that have raged for months, the chaos seemed never to end. Bloody clashes with police forces, tear gas, hooded vandals, broken windows and graffiti were a daily event.… [+1856 chars]
